        Meri kaun ho tum


meri zindagi ki nai aash ho tum,
pyar ki pahali ahasas ho tum,
meri zindagi ka suryodhay aur suryasth ho tum,
registhaan jaisi meri is zindagi me,
barish ka ahasas ho tum,
meri pyash ho tum,
meri zindagi ka ullas ho tum,
sote jagte har waqt tumara hi kayal rahat hai,
tum hi meri din aur raat ho tum,
tapti dopahari me, thandi hawaon ka ahasas ho tum,
tujhe pane ke aalawa aur koi khwais nahi,
meri zindagi ki aakhari talash ho tum,
tere chehare jaisa sundar aur koi dhrishya nahi,
tumhi mera chandani aur  meri mahatab ho tum,
tere bina har pal ek muddat ke hai barabar,
wo besbar intejar ho tum,
tujse dur jo mujhe sone na de wo khwab ho tum,
is dil me tere siwa aur koi nahi,
is dharakate hue dil ki aawaj ho tum,
lafjho me kaise bayan karu,
ki meri kaun ho tum,
meri duniya, mera abhiman ho tum,
mera pahala pyar, meri muskan ho tum,
jiska mujhe meri zindagi me hai intejar,
wo meri mohabbat, meri jaan ho tum
kiase kahun ki kau ho tum,
meri shesh zindagi ka aadhar ho tum,
tumhe panno pe likh pana mumkin nahi,
mere liye pura bramaand ho tum,
kiase kahun ki kau ho tum,
meri zindagi ki nai aash, pyar ka ahasas ho tum.
######################################################################

Tumari muskan mere har gam ke ilaj ka tarika lagata hai,
iske aage duniya ka har jewar fika lagta hai,

teri muskan ke aage duniya ka har chij nagawara lagta hai,
ye beshkimati chij chupa ke rak lu kahi, aisa lagta hai.

jab tu video call pe muskara ke Hi kahati hai,
duniya ki har khushi iske aage fiki lagti hai,

Tumare honth mujhe amrit ka pyaala lagta hai,
ise pikar mai diwana ban gaya hu, aisa lagta hai,

Tumare honth mujhe sahad ke samandar lagte hai,
jo meri pyas bujha de aise tarike lagte hai.

khuli zulfhon me tum aur bhi kahar dhathi ho,
mujpe kuch to raham karo, mujhe kitna tadpati ho.

ji karta hai ki mai tumare zulfho ke niche leta rahu,
bas tumhe dekta rahu aur zindagi gujar jaye aur kuch na karu.

dekh ke aapki muskarahat, hum hosh gawa baithe,
hosh me aane hi wale the ki aap fir se muskara baithe.




